> **From Zero to First Revenue — Revised Launch Playbook**
> Launch Target: Q2 2026 | First Revenue Target: 90 Days
> Prepared: March 31, 2026 | CONFIDENTIAL

-----

## Executive Summary

This plan replaces the broad strategy document with a sequenced, day-by-day execution roadmap. Every action is ordered by dependency — what must happen before what — not by topic. The plan is structured around one principle: **the only actions that generate first revenue are personal relationships and phone calls. Everything else is infrastructure to support those conversations.**

- **Target:** First closed charter booking within 90 days. First €10,000+ in commission within 6 months. $500K annual run rate by Month 18–24.
- **Operating assumption:** Solo founder. No employees until Month 6+ revenue validates hiring. Every hour must be allocated to the highest-leverage activity available that day.

